Sinesis and Sinister woke up. Sinesis held his head.

"Do you have a headache too?" Sinister asked.

"yeah, this stuff sucks." Sinesis said, dropping an empty wine bottle.

"I'd rather have brainfreeze!" Sinister said. Sinesis walked around and fell
over. Sinister laughed and fell out of the chair. They both stood up and
groggily and with headache looked at each other.

"What're you looking at?" Sinesis asked.

"I'm looking at Thee king." Sinister said.

"Where!" Sinesis said.

"Naaaa I don't know!" Sinister said. They both walked around, feeling pretty
bad. They seen Quickstrike, but just looked at him.

"That wine went bad!" Sinesis said...
